Starstorm/Windlord:

Windlord looked a pod nearest to Maximal base, so he landed and 
carefully left the wounded bot on floor "WingRazor, can you care 
him??? I'll check the pod" Windlord was ready to attack just in case 
that an ambush started, he looked the Pod and waited

***********************

Meanwhile, Starstorm located the pod that was near her base. "I 
locate the pod.... come to cover me!!!" She knew what to do so she 
typed the pred's activationj code and started to reprogram the 
protophor as pred.
